<!-- body start HEADER -->
  <div class="container">

    <strong><p class='flowtext' style='font-size: 18px;'>Welcome to Vancouver Tech Web! We’re a one stop shop for all things Vancouver tech. With such a booming tech industry in this beautiful city we decided to create a place where tech afficianados, investors, job hunters and those just generally interested to get all their information about the tech scene in Vancouver from one great place.</p></strong>

    <br>

  <!-- tri info -->
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col m4" style="text-align:center;">
        <i class="material-icons center-text large padded-content" style="color:#00acc1;">location_city</i>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">Seek out Companies that are thriving in this ever expanding tech culture. Use our filter to find Companies you're looking for, or learn more about some companies you might just be hearing about for the first time. Head over to the profile page of any company for more in depth information about them. See where they are located, how many people are working there and what tech stack they are working on, also visit their website or follow them on Twitter. If you're here to promote your own company, feel free to add your own exciting startup and help us build this growing community even more.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col m4" style="text-align:center;">
        <i class="material-icons center-text large padded-content" style="color:#00acc1;">developer_board</i>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">Interested in meetups and events? Why not check out our Events page and see what's coming up on the calendar for your favorite companies. You'll be able to see all upcoming events scheduled for any companies we're keeping track of. Check out the Events link and register to attend them. If you've added your own company to the site, we'll also track and plot all of your meetups and events on the calendar for all VTW users to find as well. With networking being such an important facet of the tech community, having a place to keep track of all the best opportunities is a no brainer!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col m4" style="text-align:center;">
        <i class="material-icons center-text large padded-content" style="color:#00acc1;">whatshot</i>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">Wondering what's been going on in the industry in general? Head over to our News section to discover all the latest stories coming our from any of the great businesses we are tracking. It can be tough to seek out news so we thought it would be great to have it all available for you in real time on one hub. Don't miss out on any more information at VTW, you'll be able to stay in touch in this rapidly evolving space and can be right on the tip of the spear with any new developments. Our news feed will keep you up to date with your favorite companies and let you touch base with new companies for the first time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <br>
    <br>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col s12">
        <img class='responsive-img' src="https://cdn0.tnwcdn.com/wp-content/blogs.dir/1/files/2016/05/tech-job.jpg" alt="">
      </div>

      <div class="col s12">
        <h4>Mission Statement</h4>
        <p class='justify'>Our mission is simple: Make keeping track of technology companies in Vancouver an easy and fun endeavor. Too many times we have seen other sites fail to hit the mark on providing a cohesive solution for keeping tabs on the blossoming tech business scene in this great city. We set out to make VTW a catch all website for businesses new and old to be researched, followed and contacted from one easy to use place.</p>
        <p class='justify'>We won’t make you feel like it's too daunting to get the info you want and need about all these fantastic companies. We strive to make an engaging interface integrate seamlessly with all things Vancouver tech.  When Vancouver tech business grows ours will scale right along with them, therefore, we will work hand in hand with them and with our users to support this ever growing ecosystem.</p>
        <p class='justify'>We strive to develop a superior Internet portal experience for our users through state-of-the-art technology, innovation, community engagement and partnerships.</p>
      </div>
